OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777911070
OL,3,CCar collides into pub garden leaving
OL,4,Ctrail of destruction
OL,6,FA pub in the New Forest, that was
OL,7,Fforced to close after extensive flood
OL,8,Fdamage, has faced another setback.
OL,10,FThe Woolpack in Sopley had to shut in
OL,11,FJanuary during Storm Chandra.
OL,13,FAfter the start of an extensive
OL,14,Frefurbishment, it was due to re-open
OL,15,Fin March, but more heavy rain left it
OL,16,Funder water again.
OL,18,FNow, just a month before it was set to
OL,19,Fwelcome back customers, a car has
OL,20,Fcollided into its garden, causing
OL,21,Fsevere damage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
