OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777911070
OL,3,CCar collides into pub garden leaving
OL,4,Ctrail of destruction
OL,6,FHampshire Police were called at 4am
OL,7,FMonday 4 May to reports of a single-
OL,8,Fvehicle collision on Ringwood Road.
OL,10,FThe vehicle was also badly damaged and
OL,11,Fhad to be lifted up by specialist
OL,12,Fequipment.
OL,14,FNobody was injured in the crash.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
