OL,3,CCar collides into pub garden leaving
OL,4,Ctrail of destruction
OL,6,FA 21-year-old from Bournemouth was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of driving
OL,8,Fwhilst unfit through drink, driving a
OL,9,Fmotor vehicle whilst unfit through
OL,10,Fdrugs, driving a motor vehicle with a
OL,11,Fproportion of a specified controlled
OL,12,Fdrug above the specified limit and
OL,13,Fdriving a motor vehicle dangerously.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
