PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777911070
OL,3,CCar collides into pub garden leaving
OL,4,Ctrail of destruction
OL,6,FA second 21-year-old, also from
OL,7,FBournemouth, was arrested on suspicion
OL,8,Fof driving whilst unfit through drink,
OL,9,Fdriving a motor vehicle whilst unfit
OL,10,Fthrough drugs, driving a motor vehicle
OL,11,Fwith a proportion of a specified
OL,12,Fcontrolled drug above the specified
OL,13,Flimit and driving a motor vehicle
OL,14,Fdangerously, and driving a motor
OL,15,Fvehicle when alcohol level above limit.
OL,17,FThe floors of The Woolpack had to be
OL,18,Fripped up following the flooding in
OL,19,FMarch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
