PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1777911070
OL,3,CCar collides into pub garden leaving
OL,4,Ctrail of destruction
OL,6,FAnd the cladding and the bar had to be
OL,7,Fdismantled so the pub could dry out
OL,8,Ffollowing the weeks of heavy rain.
OL,10,FStaff are now cleaning up the mess
OL,11,Fleft behind from the collision in the
OL,12,Fearly hours of Bank Holiday Monday.
OL,14,FA wall, along with table and chairs
OL,15,Fcan be seen smashed to pieces in
OL,16,Fphotos posted by the pub on social
OL,17,Fmedia.
OL,19,FDespite this latest incident, the pub
OL,20,Fis hopeful to be open in June.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
